      <t:profileDesc xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">
         <t:abstract><t:p>The <t:foreign xml:lang="gez">Śǝrʿāt za-ʾagbǝʾo tābota wǝsta beta krǝstiyān</t:foreign> is transmitted in 
            <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BLorient549">London, British Library, BL Oriental 549</t:ref>, <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BLorient550">London, British Library, BL Oriental 550</t:ref>, and <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BLorient788">London, British Library, BL Oriental 788</t:ref>
            together with <t:ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4020RegulaeHierarchia">Regulae
                                                  de Hierarchia ecclesiastica</t:ref>. Whether it is identical to 
            <t:ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2330serata">Śǝrʿāta beta
                                                  krǝstiyān ʾama qǝddāsehā</t:ref> remains to be determined.
         </t:p></t:abstract>
